snippet.title: Soulmask Annual Update - Wild Ride | Release Date Teaser
snippet.description:
On November 25, Soulmask will be getting its biggest update of the year: Wild Ride
which includes 4 New Mounts such as elephants, boars, gliders, sleds
Free DLC (Cozy Tribe Theme Pack)
New Breeding Creatures (horn eagles, bison, armadillo lizards, and tortoises)
New Arena NPC gameplay
New Plunderer Events gameplay
Photo Mode support, Controller optimization, and many other content updates. Stay tuned!
